     %QUERY                  - List of linked areas.
     %LINKED                 - List of linked areas.
     %UNLINKED               - List of unlinked areas.

     %AVAIL                  - List of areas available from uplinks.

     %RULES ?                - List of available conference rules.
     %RULES <AREA>           - Send rules of specified area.

     +<AREA>                 - Subscribe to specified area.
     -<AREA>                 - Unsubscribe from specified area.
     %SUB <AREA>             - Subscribe to specified area.
     %UNSUB <AREA>           - Unsubscribe from specified area.
     %+ALL                   - Subscribe to all available areas
     %-ALL                   - Unsubscribe from all areas

     %PASSIVE                - Temporatory freeze your link.
     %PAUSE                  - Temporatory freeze your link.
     %ACTIVE                 - Unfreeze your link.
     %RESUME                 - Unfreeze your link.

